data.value:
The Haptogram Designer is an application that allows the user to visually design haptograms. It is developed as a part of the EU project SUITCEYES. The overall objective of SUITCEYES is to improve the level of independence and participation of people with deafblindness and to enhance their communication, perception of the environment, knowledge acquisition and conduct of daily routines.
You can read more about the EU project at https://www.suitceyes.eu
